### FxConverter API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000

### Test Currency Conversion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100,
  "fromCurrency": "USD",
  "toCurrency": "EUR"
}

### Test Currency Conversion - Same Currency
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50,
  "fromCurrency": "USD",
  "toCurrency": "USD"
}

### Test Currency Conversion - Large Amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000,
  "fromCurrency": "GBP",
  "toCurrency": "JPY"
}

### Get Conversion History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/conversion/history?userId=default-user

### Get Available Currencies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currency

### Get Exchange Rates for USD
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currency/rates/USD

### Get Exchange Rates for EUR
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/currency/rates/EUR

### Test Invalid Currency Conversion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": -10,
  "fromCurrency": "USD",
  "toCurrency": "EUR"
}

### Test Missing Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/conversion
Content-Type: application/json

{
